        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>American Grown Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits certain agencies from procuring cut flowers or cut greens grown outside the United States. The bill also sets forth requirements for such agencies accepting gifts of cut flowers or cut greens grown outside the United States.</p> ]]>
        </text>
